descriptionHtml:
[size=5]
[/size][center][size=5]Hello! another simple Character Preset for RaceMenu
She's a DarkElf Preset her name is Leirifa one of my personal characters,
feel free to play with her as your character.[/size]
[/center]
[size=6]Requirements:[/size]

[size=3][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58221/?]KS Hairdo's[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192]Eyes of Aber
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion*[/url][/size]

[size=6]Recommended:[/size]

[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35303/?]Female Facial Animation
[/url][/size]
[size=6]Installation:[/size]

[size=3]Step-1. Download my mod and place it at Data/SKSE/plugins/CharGen/Presets

[size=3]Step-[/size]2. Start Skyrim using SKSE loader

[size=3]Step-[/size]3. Load any working save file or start a newgame

[size=3]Step-[/size]4. Open the console " ~ "

[size=3]Step-[/size]5. Type "showracemenu"

[size=3]Step-[/size]6. Select the DarkElf Race. (if you dont want to be a DarkElf choose other Race, then use "Sculpt" inside RaceMenu
            then click "Import Head" choose "DarkElf Leirifa Head" do this after "Step-7 and Step-8".)

[size=3]Step-[/size]7. Look for "Preset" inside RaceMenu

[size=3]Step-[/size]8. Press F9, then click "DarkElf Leirifa"

[size=3]Step-[/size]9. Play! have fun... :D[/size]
author: iPresets
